Privacy Policy for App.
Effective Date: June 25, 2025
Learn Finance Now is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what limited information we collect and how we use it.
1. Information We Collect
We only collect information directly from you when you voluntarily use the "Contact Us" form located on your "Your Profile" page within the App.
â€¢	Information You Provide Directly: 
o	Email Address: We collect the email address you provide in the form.
o	Message Content: We collect the message you send us through the form.
We do not collect any other personal information about you. We do not track your usage, collect device information, or use third-party analytics tools.
2. How We Use Your Information
The sole purpose for collecting your email address and message content is to enable us to communicate with you in response to your inquiry or feedback.
3. Sharing Your Information
We do not share any of your information with third parties. Your email address and message are used exclusively by Learn Finance Now for the purpose of responding to your direct communication.
4. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect the limited information we collect from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, please be aware that no security system is entirely impenetrable.
5. Children's Privacy
Our App is intended for a general audience and not specifically directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Effective Date" at the top. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
